Even Had 370 Million Reais in Third Quarter Contracted Sales

-- B y   F a b i o l a   M o u r a
-- 
2011-10-17T22:06:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/even-had-370-million-reais-in-third-quarter-contracted-sales.html
Even Construtora e Incorporadora SA (EVEN3) 
said it had 370 million reais in contracted sales in the third
quarter. The Sao Paulo-based homebuilder said it also started
448 million reais in new projects in the same period. The
company announced its preliminary sales in a regulatory filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabiola Moura in New York at 
 fdemoura@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
